revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Categories and interwikis go at the bottom of this page. -->

Specify the language to link to the key for a specific language, as in:
:<code><nowiki>{{WikiIPA|French}}</nowiki></code>
which yields:
:{{WikiIPA|French}}
If the key subpage name differs from the language name, specify a second parameter, as in:
:<code><nowiki>{{WikiIPA|Urdu|Hindi and Urdu}}</nowiki></code>
which yields:
:{{WikiIPA|Urdu|Hindi and Urdu}}

